&lt;p&gt;Launched in 2015, we are scaling fast and moving in exciting directions. We have been included in KPMG’s Global Fintech 100, listed at the top of Forbes&#39; list of socially-responsible startups, and profiled by the &lt;em&gt;Financial Times&lt;/em&gt; and &lt;em&gt;The Times&lt;/em&gt;. Co-founded by entrepreneurs Asesh Sarkar, Daniel Shakhani, and Dan Cobley (former Head of Google UK &amp;amp; Ireland), we are proud to be authorised by the FCA and making a meaningful impact on people’s lives.&lt;/p&gt;
